kground:#bb8b2a; color: #000000;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: New York (season 7)|7]]\n| {{Start date|2016|11|21}}\n| {{End date|2017|2|27}}\n| 2.40\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2017\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: Atlanta]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#ccb68f; color: #000000;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: Atlanta (season 6)|6]]\n| {{Start date|2017|3|6}}\n| {{End date|2017|7|17}}\n| 2.74\n|-\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: Hollywood]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#f1efe5; color: #000000;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: Hollywood (season 4)|4]]\n| {{Start date|2017|7|24}}\n| {{End date|2017|10|23}}\n| 2.02\n|-\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: New York]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#000000; color: #000000;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: New York (season 8)|8]]\n| {{Start date|2017|10|30}}\n| {{End date|2018|3|12}}\n| 1.81\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2018\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: Miami]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FF7F50; color: #000000;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: Miami (season 1)|1]]\n| {{Start date|2018|1|1}}\n| {{End date|2018|3|19}}\n| 1.72\n|-\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: Atlanta]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#271039; color: #000000;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: Atlanta (season 7)|7]]\n| {{Start date|2018|3|19}}\n| {{End date|2018|7|16}}\n| 2.05\n|-\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: Hollywood]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#a2cacf; color: #000000;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: Hollywood (season 5)|5]]\n| {{Start date|2018|7|23}}\n| {{End date|2018|11|19}}\n| 1.90\n|-\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: New York]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#37302c; color: #37302c;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: New York (season 9)|9]]\n| {{Start date|2018|11|26}}\n| {{End date|2019|3|18}}\n| 1.41\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2019\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: Miami]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#e9ab50; color: #F66A60;\"|\n| [[Love & Hip Hop: Miami (season 2)|2]]\n| {{Start date|2019|1|2}}\n| {{End date|2019|3|25}}\n| 1.05\n|-\n| ''[[Love & Hip Hop: Atlanta]]''\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#2a218a; color: #2a218a;\"|\n| [